## рџ“Њ Project Overview

This project is an industry-level full-stack web application built using Flask (Python) that performs:

- Data Validation (Regex-based)
- Data Processing (Pandas & NumPy)
- Data Analysis
- Data Visualization (Matplotlib & Chart.js)
- Concurrent Processing (Multithreading & Multiprocessing)

The application provides a modern dashboard UI for uploading datasets, analyzing them, and visualizing insights in real-time.

